<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />May they be like the grass on the housetops</para>

<para style="q1">that withers before it grows up,</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />that cannot fill the reaper's hand</para>

<para style="q1">or the chest of the one who binds sheaves.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />May those who pass by not say,</para>

<para style="q1">"May the blessing of Yahweh be on you;</para>

<para style="q1">we bless you in the name of Yahweh."</para>
